_d%27animaux_de_compagnie_au_Royaume-Uni_en_1939","langname":"French","autonym":"fran\u00e7ais","*":"Massacre d'animaux de compagnie au Royaume-Uni en 1939"},{"lang":"he","url":"https://he.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D7%94%D7%9E%D7%AA%D7%AA_%D7%97%D7%99%D7%95%D7%AA_%D7%94%D7%9E%D7%97%D7%9E%D7%93_%D7%91%D7%91%D7%A8%D7%99%D7%98%D7%A0%D7%99%D7%94,_1939","langname":"Hebrew","autonym":"\u05e2\u05d1\u05e8\u05d9\u05ea","*":"\u05d4\u05de\u05ea\u05ea \u05d7\u05d9\u05d5\u05ea \u05d4\u05de\u05d7\u05de\u05d3 \u05d1\u05d1\u05e8\u05d9\u05d8\u05e0\u05d9\u05d4, 1939"},{"lang":"ja","url":"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%A4%E3%82%AE%E3%83%AA%E3%82%B9%E3%81%AB%E3%81%8A%E3%81%91%E3%82%8B%E3%83%9A%E3%83%83%E3%83%88%E3%81%AE%E6%88%A6%E6%99%82%E6%AE%BA%E5%87%A6%E5%88%86","langname":"Japanese","autonym":"\u65e5\u672c\u8a9e","*":"\u30a4\u30ae\u30ea\u30b9\u306b\u304a\u3051\u308b\u30da\u30c3\u30c8\u306e\u6226\u6642\u6bba\u51e6\u5206"},{"lang":"ru","url":"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%91%D1%80%D0%B8%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BD%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B8%D0%B9_%D1%85%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%BE%D0%BA%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%82_%D0%B6%D0%B8%D0%B2%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%BD%D1%8B%D1%85","langname":"Russian","autonym":"\u0440\u0443\u0441\u0441\u043a\u0438\u0439","*":"\u0411\u0440\u0438\u0442\u0430\u043d\u0441\u043a\u0438\u0439 \u0445\u043e\u043b\u043e\u043a\u043e\u0441\u0442 \u0436\u0438\u0432\u043e\u0442\u043d\u044b\u0445"}],"categories":[{"sortkey":"","hidden":"","*":"Use_dmy_dates_from_September_2016"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Animal_cruelty_incidents"},{"sortkey":"Pet massacre","*":"Animal_welfare_and_rights_in_the_United_Kingdom"},{"sortkey":"","*":"1939_in_the_United_Kingdom"},{"sortkey":"","*":"United_Kingdom_home_front_during_World_War_II"},{"sortkey":"Pets","*":"Massacres_committed_by_the_United_Kingdom"},{"sortkey":"Massacre","*":"Pets_in_the_United_Kingdom"}],"links":[{"ns":14,"exists":"","*":"Category:Use dmy dates from September 2016"},{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Air Raid Precautions"},{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Battersea Dogs & Cats Home"}